119
0:05:05.26,000 --> 0:05:08,000
They're as smart as chimpanzees in some respects.

120
0:05:08.26,000 --> 0:05:1,000
And this is a bird on the cover of science

121
0:05:10.26,000 --> 0:05:13,000
who's learned how to use a tool to get food.

122
0:05:13.26,000 --> 0:05:15,000
On the other hand,

123
0:05:15.26,000 --> 0:05:17,000
we have our friend the domestic chicken.

124
0:05:17.26,000 --> 0:05:2,000
And chickens and ducks and geese and turkeys

125
0:05:20.26,000 --> 0:05:22,000
are basically as dumb as dumps.

126
0:05:22.26,000 --> 0:05:25,000
So they're very, very good at pecking for grain,

127
0:05:25.26,000 --> 0:05:28,000
