128
0:05:28.26,000 --> 0:05:3,000
Well it turns out that the babies,

129
0:05:30.26,000 --> 0:05:32,000
the New Caledonian crow babies, are fledglings.

130
0:05:32.26,000 --> 0:05:34,000
They depend on their moms

131
0:05:34.26,000 --> 0:05:37,000
