134
0:05:41.26,000 --> 0:05:43,000
Whereas the chickens are actually mature

135
0:05:43.26,000 --> 0:05:45,000
within a couple of months.

136
0:05:45.26,000 --> 0:05:48,000
So childhood is the reason

137
0:05:48.26,000 --> 0:05:5,000
why the crows end up on the cover of Science

138
0:05:50.26,000 --> 0:05:52,000
and the chickens end up in the soup pot.

139
0:05:52.26,000 --> 0:05:55,000
There's something about that long childhood

140
0:05:55.26,000 --> 0:05:57,000
that seems to be connected

141
0:05:57.26,000 --> 0:05:59,000
to knowledge and learning.

142
0:05:59.26,000 --> 0:06:02,000
Well what kind of explanation could we have for this?

143
0:06:02.26,000 --> 0:06:05,000
Well some animals, like the chicken,

144
0:06:05.26,000 --> 0:06:07,000
seem to be beautifully suited

145
0:06:07.26,000 --> 0:06:09,000
to doing just one thing very well.

146
0:06:09.26,000 --> 0:06:12,000
