166
0:06:54.26,000 --> 0:06:57,000
into those little open mouths.

167
0:06:57.26,000 --> 0:07:,000
All right, why would we see this correlation?

168
0:07:00.26,000 --> 0:07:04,000
Well an idea is that that strategy, that learning strategy,

169
0:07:04.26,000 --> 0:07:07,000
is an extremely powerful, great strategy for getting on in the world,

170
0:07:07.26,000 --> 0:07:09,000
but it has one big disadvantage.

171
0:07:09.26,000 --> 0:07:11,000
And that one big disadvantage

172
0:07:11.26,000 --> 0:07:14,000
